    },
    {
      "start": 662.27,
      "end": 662.49,
      "text": "투"
    },
    {
      "start": 662.49,
      "end": 663.29,
      "text": "그쵸"
    },
    {
      "start": 663.29,
      "end": 665.27,
      "text": "Well they had to tear it down"
    },
    {
      "start": 665.27,
      "end": 666.43,
      "text": "after the shoot"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.43,
      "end": 668.13,
      "text": "촬영이 끝나고 나서"
    },
    {
      "start": 668.13,
      "end": 669.63,
      "text": "they had to tear it down"
    },
    {
      "start": 669.63,
      "end": 671.07,
      "text": "철거해야 했어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 671.07,
      "end": 673.99,
      "text": "Bergman was looking for a small garden"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.99,
      "end": 675.17,
      "text": "with old trees"
    },
    {
      "start": 675.17,
      "end": 676.95,
      "text": "And that's part of why"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.95,
      "end": 678.41,
      "text": "he picked this spot"
    },
    {
      "start": 678.41,
      "end": 680.19,
      "text": "베르만 감독은"
    },
    {
      "start": 680.19,
      "end": 681.43,
      "text": "was looking for"
    },
    {
      "start": 681.43,
      "end": 682.67,
      "text": "찾고 있었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 682.67,
      "end": 683.97,
      "text": "A small garden"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.97,
      "end": 685.25,
      "text": "with old trees"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.25,
      "end": 687.73,
      "text": "작은 정원을 찾고 있었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 687.73,
      "end": 688.63,
      "text": "그 정원 속에"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.63,
      "end": 690.93,
      "text": "오래된 나무들이 있었어야 됐나봐요"
    },
    {
      "start": 690.93,
      "end": 692.45,
      "text": "고목을 찾고 있었대요"
    },
    {
      "start": 692.45,
      "end": 693.97,
      "text": "And that's part of why"
    },
    {
      "start": 693.97,
      "end": 695.13,
      "text": "he picked his spot"
    },
    {
      "start": 695.13,
      "end": 697.91,
      "text": "그래서 그가 이 장소를 택한 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 697.91,
      "end": 700.11,
      "text": "The trees are still here"
    },
    {
      "start": 700.11,
      "end": 701.59,
      "text": "and you can also see"
    },
    {
      "start": 701.59,
      "end": 703.47,
      "text": "where they took down the wall"
    },
    {
      "start": 703.47,
      "end": 705.25,
      "text": "그 나무들은"
    },
    {
      "start": 705.25,
      "end": 706.45,
      "text": "are still here"
    },
    {
      "start": 706.45,
      "end": 708.57,
      "text": "여전히 그대로 여기에 있고"
    },
    {
      "start": 708.57,
      "end": 709.99,
      "text": "and you can also see"
    },
    {
      "start": 709.99,
      "end": 711.75,
      "text": "where they took down the wall"
    },
    {
      "start": 711.75,
      "end": 713.53,
      "text": "여러분들은"
    },
    {
      "start": 713.53,
      "end": 715.35,
      "text": "담을 허문 흔적도"
    },
    {
      "start": 715.35,
      "end": 716.53,
      "text": "역시 볼 수 있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 716.53,
      "end": 729.35,
      "text": "흔적을 보면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 729.35,
      "end": 730.81,
      "text": "그의 발자취"
    },
    {
      "start": 730.81,
      "end": 732.53,
      "text": "역사적인 발자취를"
    },
    {
      "start": 732.53,
      "end": 733.25,
      "text": "따라가는 것도"
    },
    {
      "start": 733.25,
      "end": 734.93,
      "text": "되게 의미 있는 일이라고 봅니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 734.93,
      "end": 736.61,
      "text": "This is a fun kind of trip"
    },
    {
      "start": 736.61,
      "end": 738.67,
      "text": "to find remnants of something"
    },
    {
      "start": 738.67,
      "end": 740.15,
      "text": "It's like a treasure hunt"
    },
    {
      "start": 740.15,
      "end": 742.79,
      "text": "Yeah, 보물찾기 같은 느낌도 들고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 742.79,
      "end": 744.49,
      "text": "그럼 한 번 더 들어보시죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 744.49,
      "end": 747.97,
      "text": "The house and the film was here"
    },
    {
      "start": 747.97,
      "end": 750.65,
      "text": "Actually, they only built the facade"
    },
    {
      "start": 750.65,
      "end": 753.01,
      "text": "and the interiors were mostly shot in studio"
    },
    {
      "start": 753.01,
      "end": 754.39,
      "text": "What happened to the house?"
    },
    {
      "start": 754.61,
      "end": 756.21,
      "text": "Well, they had to tear it down"
    },
    {
      "start": 756.21,
      "end": 756.99,
      "text": "after the shoot"
    },
    {
      "start": 756.99,
      "end": 760.58,
      "text": "Bergman was looking for a small garden"
    },
    {
      "start": 760.58,
      "end": 761.58,
      "text": "with all trees"
    },
    {
      "start": 761.58,
      "end": 762.66,
      "text": "and that's part of why"
    },
    {
      "start": 762.66,
      "end": 763.56,
      "text": "he picked the spot"
    },
    {
      "start": 763.56,
      "end": 765.24,
      "text": "The trees are still here"
    },
    {
      "start": 765.24,
      "end": 766.58,
      "text": "and you can also see"
    },
    {
      "start": 766.58,
      "end": 767.74,
      "text": "where they took down the wall"
    },
    {
      "start": 767.74,
      "end": 770.55,
      "text": "잘 확인해 보셨고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 770.55,
      "end": 771.99,
      "text": "양진영 님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 771.99,
      "end": 773.85,
      "text": "조크쌤과 함께하는"
    },
    {
      "start": 773.85,
      "end": 775.41,
      "text": "이 시간이 너무 소중해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 775.41,
      "end": 776.93,
      "text": "또 아쉬운 마음이네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 776.93,
      "end": 777.69,
      "text": "You, you"
    },
    {
      "start": 777.69,
      "end": 779.23,
      "text": "Oh, don't cry"
    },
    {
      "start": 779.23,
      "end": 780.67,
      "text": "그래도 우리"
    },
    {
      "start": 780.67,
      "end": 782.29,
      "text": "It ain't over till it's over"
    },
    {
      "start": 782.29,
      "end": 783.59,
      "text": "Oh, it ain't over till it's over"
    },
    {
      "start": 783.59,
      "end": 785.23,
      "text": "명언이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 785.23,
      "end": 785.85,
      "text": "그렇죠, 그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 785.85,
      "end": 787.01,
      "text": "But still, very sad"
    },
    {
      "start": 787.01,
      "end": 787.43,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 787.43,
      "end": 788.27,
      "text": "Joke chemistry?"
    },
    {
      "start": 788.61,
      "end": 789.81,
      "text": "Where's it gonna go?"
    },
    {
      "start": 790.61,
      "end": 791.81,
      "text": "기대해 보도록 하겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 791.81,
      "end": 792.27,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 792.27,
      "end": 793.95,
      "text": "그래도 우리가"
    },
    {
      "start": 793.95,
      "end": 795.27,
      "text": "6월 영화 끝까지"
    },
    {
      "start": 795.27,
      "end": 797.47,
      "text": "함께해 주시길 바라는 마음이고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 797.47,
      "end": 798.31,
      "text": "우리 크쌤은"
    },
    {
      "start": 798.31,
      "end": 798.97,
      "text": "See you tomorrow"
    },
    {
      "start": 798.97,
      "end": 799.97,
      "text": "I'll see you then"
    }
  ]
}